{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.200", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.160", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eAbgasversuche an Menschen und Affen\u201c ist das Thema, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.640", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eingebracht von B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.200", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein sehr rei\u00dferischer Titel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.080", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was steckt nun eigentlich dahinter? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.400", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zwei unterschiedliche Sachverhalte werden hier in einer unverantwortlichen Art und Weise miteinander vermischt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.680", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum einen die Tierversuche mit Abgasen und zum anderen ein Probandenversuch an der Uniklinik in Aachen mit reinem Stickstoffdioxid."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.440", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was ist wirklich passiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.880", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.440", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darauf will ich n\u00e4her eingehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.240", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Institut f\u00fcr Arbeits-, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.960", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sozial- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.920", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Umweltmedizin der Rheinisch-Westf\u00e4lischen Technischen Hochschule Aachen unter der Leitung von Professor Thomas Kraus erkl\u00e4rt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Initiative zu diesem Test kam vonseiten der Senatskommission der Deutschen Forschungsgemeinschaft im Rahmen der damaligen Diskussion zur \u00c4nderung von Grenzwerten an Arbeitspl\u00e4tzen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.400", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht im Stra\u00dfenverkehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.320", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht mit Autos, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.120", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern an Arbeitspl\u00e4tzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Studie war ein Teil einer neuen Auflage mit feineren Messmethoden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.960", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man wollte reines Stickstoffdioxid auf seine Wirkung testen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.480", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Probanden wurden geringen und kurzzeitigen Belastungen mit Stickstoffdioxid ausgesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.520", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist Fakt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.760", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was hei\u00dft \u201egering\u201c? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.600", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eGering\u201c hei\u00dft: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.560", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unter den Werten von 40\u00a0Mikrogramm pro Kubikmeter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.360", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eKurzzeitig\u201c hei\u00dft: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.960", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kleiner 1\u00a0Stunde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.840", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Europ\u00e4ische Forschungsvereinigung f\u00fcr Umwelt und Gesundheit im Transportsektor\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.120", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wurde eben schon angesprochen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.680", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "finanziert von VW, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.960", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daimler und BMW, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.560", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat das finanziert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um eine Belastung am Arbeitsplatz zu untersuchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.840", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollten die Werte wissen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.240", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu dieser indirekten Finanzierung der Studie sagt Professor Kraus von der RWTH Aachen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.160", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Autokonzerne h\u00e4tten keinen Einfluss auf den Versuch oder die Interpretation der Ergebnisse gehabt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.960", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Erkl\u00e4rung m\u00fcssen wir erst einmal so hinnehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.400", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ging um eine Studie an Menschen mit reinem Stickstoffdioxid, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Grenzwerte f\u00fcr Belastungen am Arbeitsplatz zu ermitteln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.720", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "25\u00a0Personen wurden einem Test unterhalb des Grenzwertes ausgesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.440", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht also nicht um Abgase aus Dieselmotoren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.560", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das m\u00fcssen wir unterscheiden\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.320", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern allein um reines Stickstoffdioxid. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.720", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Abgase aus einem Dieselmotor enthalten wesentlich mehr Schadstoffe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.960", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Versuche an Probanden sind nichts Neues. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.680", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie wir gerade geh\u00f6rt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.360", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unterziehen sich Zehntausende Probanden per annum freiwillig Versuchen in der Medizintechnik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.560", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist auch festzustellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Studie vor dem Dieselskandal initiiert wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.680", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es besteht auch kein Zusammenhang mit den in den USA durchgef\u00fchrten Versuchen an Tieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.280", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumindest nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.560", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was die in Rede stehende Studie in Aachen betrifft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.480", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nun ein sehr wichtiger Punkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.000", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den schon die Vorrednerin angesprochen hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.840", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt eine Ethikkommission. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese hat zum Beispiel nach \u00a7\u00a040 Absatz\u00a01 des Arzneimittelgesetzes und \u00a7\u00a020 des Medizinproduktegesetzes eine klare Aufgabe und Struktur. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.480", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie besteht aus \u00c4rzten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.480", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Juristen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.280", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pharmakologen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.960", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Apothekern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.400", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ethikern usw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.640", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie ber\u00e4t \u00c4rzte bei Versuchen und hat auch das Recht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.080", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.200", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Versuch darf nicht durchgef\u00fchrt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.280", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Genehmigung eines Versuchs m\u00fcssen zwei wesentliche Kriterien erf\u00fcllt sein: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.080", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erstens keine wesentlichen gesundheitlichen Sch\u00e4den bei den Probanden und zweitens Freiwilligkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.200", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern verst\u00f6\u00dft die in Rede stehende Studie bei aller Kritik nicht gegen geltendes Recht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.000", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn solche Versuche als kritikw\u00fcrdig anzusehen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.400", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss das Recht ge\u00e4ndert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.000", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jedenfalls hat man sich in Aachen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.080", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gemessen an der Gesetzeslage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.040", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht str\u00e4flich falsch verhalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.720", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Vorw\u00fcrfe gegen\u00fcber der Rheinisch-Westf\u00e4lischen TH Aachen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.280", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Europ\u00e4ischen Forschungsvereinigung oder der Autoindustrie sind aus meiner Sicht nichts anderes als der Versuch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.880", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen Skandal ohne Substanz aufzubauen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.800", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich beziehe mich hierbei auf die Studie in Aachen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.520", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Vorw\u00fcrfe sind ohne Substanz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.880", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier hat man sich im Rahmen des geltenden Rechts bewegt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.600", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man solche Studien f\u00fcr falsch h\u00e4lt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.640", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss man das geltende Recht \u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.440", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Wissenschaftler haben sich jedenfalls im Rechtsrahmen bewegt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.440", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Kritik ist undifferenziert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.320", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da sie unverantwortlicherweise suggeriert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.640", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass in Deutschland Abgasversuche an Menschen durchgef\u00fchrt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.040", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das waren keine Abgase, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.640", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie das darlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.600", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern das war ein Gas."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.600", 
